Assumptions and Dependencies
It was confirmed that there is currently no function to control the Inhibit information of the ORU ALD alarm by providing a function as
a method of controlling the Inhibit information of the AlarmItem.
Since it is necessary to control whether to report AlarmItem, it is necessary to consider the related functions, suppression keep mode,
flooding, and ne unit inhibition operation.
Both FM/AM are required to be deployed in the FM_FEL as a feature that must be provided.
